{"tid":456733,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[每日更新] 戒煙2017","createTime":"2017-11-03T07:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T08:03:06.000Z","uid":155398,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d9dc7d9bff679a0a5153c55457cf135ea47d81f3","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n年幾前同拍左幾年拖既初戀散左<br />\n有一晚同個朋友落左街吹水<br />\n問佢拎左支黑冰8食 開頭都唔識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來我學識左 吸一啖入口再抖啖條落肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個下好暈，種感覺好難忘<br />\n之後第2日就已經心郁想買包<br />\n雖然冇癮 但唔知點解好想買籓試<br />\n咁就踏上左食煙之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個排好頹好灰，夜晚得番自己個時點起支煙<br />\n噴每一啖都想煩惱隨住啲煙煙消雲散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個咁傻豬既諗法係呃人的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本冇用<br />\n本來都覺得自己冇咩煙癮<br />\n到有日一訓醒忽然好想食就自奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係幾個月前我同左現任一齊<br />\n佢未同我一齊已經知我食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我同自己講點想食都好唔可以係佢面前食<br />\n到一齊左一段時間 佢有晚攬住我同我講:我唔想你再食煙<br />\n個下唔知點解好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自始之後我食少左 由一日5~6支變到一日2~3支<br />\n但都未完全戒得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n趁煙癮唔算深，我決定由今日開始一支都唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經研究過幾時最易戒煙失敗<br />\n<br />\n1.番工冇野做<br />\n2.一起身<br />\n3.女朋友唔係我身邊<br />\n4.落bar<br />\n<br />\n所以我已經掉哂所有火機同煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔落bar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買定好多薯片到想食煙就食薯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎各位講下仲有咩方法<br />\n<br />\n此POST每日更新，希望各位見到呢個POST都可以一齊戒<br />\n諗下屋企人同錫你既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"47726b3142d9926790eb3a94211c879af0429e38","tid":456733,"uid":2247,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:01:37.000Z","msg":"食口煙先講啦"},{"pid":"059dc1c85646fd0f8d71e98117977ba468db952a","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食口煙先講啦</blockquote><br />\n有冇追POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 掉哂所有煙同火機啦了"},{"pid":"56c473cf009807f3419d82d795d81e14708118b6","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e5c0cccc388ec1649ba4830295cc1f0f170aa8","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:08:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4e035f848e3e4a5f496fb8f3124f1ddf4a7d81e","tid":456733,"uid":8726,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:11:22.000Z","msg":"扮咩清泉 拿拿林買番包一齊煲"},{"pid":"253114df3257b2fed75c70c8694218865d2f1256","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮咩清泉 拿拿林買番包一齊煲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔會咁易動搖(住)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a969d93684d917d3d46639a81691f2e8079cde","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a467e9417626157a4ad687a328c009330bfbe535","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34f89d2173072cbb9dc436de6bfd476c2e9d583","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:36:16.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2369740815922c4bb23145b52a2ef79415f84784","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"837509ee086843862bfe2b1b9f9abbf1b097ed41","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"026f73f9a0b7bdaa76afc521d1e44976a6bd9ed5","tid":456733,"uid":122115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:10:02.000Z","msg":"巴打一齊加油"},{"pid":"08292ef1c5b12a468c3f64676801d792995c5fc9","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打一齊加油</blockquote><br />\n共勉之 每日上黎報到"},{"pid":"3078a0c2fbbd075203c5cd71f0cc32e66a3bb6fb","tid":456733,"uid":4254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:23:42.000Z","msg":"加油！有啲野真係只係習慣<br />\n<br />\n利申已戒 但每逢唱k，bar呢啲地方就會心郁 <br />\n同埋身邊朋友都食緊時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發覺都係夜晚嘅時候"},{"pid":"df16085325db7e50a54d871aa01194b2167de99d","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加油！有啲野真係只係習慣<br />\n<br />\n利申已戒 但每逢唱k，bar呢啲地方就會心郁 <br />\n同埋身邊朋友都食緊時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發覺都係夜晚嘅時候</blockquote><br />\n 我都分唔清係習慣定癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一早起身想食應該係癮 落bar係習慣"},{"pid":"c0b14b31324c913dec0abdf988a57682e5e29330","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043d7bb12bc76ba96373eab78275b35359dc00c0","tid":456733,"uid":122115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"而家一星期一枝 本身一日七八枝 同巴打一樣 失戀之後就開始食 一開始以為自己唔會上癮 點知有次食完飯係街行行下 入左7仔買煙食 好想戒煙 因為食煙會令人有抑鬱 根本就唔會有飄飄然既感覺 果啲只係尼古丁呃緊你個大腦 愈食個人愈唔開心"},{"pid":"36fd98e0ea0bdcdaf16f75ab040e38108f9654e8","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家一星期一枝 本身一日七八枝 同巴打一樣 失戀之後就開始食 一開始以為自己唔會上癮 點知有次食完飯係街行行下 入左7仔買煙食 好想戒煙 因為食煙會令人有抑鬱 根本就唔會有飄飄然既感覺 果啲只係尼古丁呃緊你個大腦 愈食個人愈唔開心</blockquote><br />\n我諗唔少人因為感情問題食第一支<br />\n一齊唔好食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你並不孤單"},{"pid":"d49aa4f61bc0af2ff2810295da0077be9a429ba7","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbafe25560698e67b6210262856c2eec422dc4c7","tid":456733,"uid":17223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"我都想戒 有一排食少左 但慢慢又食多返"},{"pid":"afff7cfaa393314072865883e5478c07cb81252a","tid":456733,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"同現任散左 又食返"},{"pid":"6a5461fb0d664af0da734318f6d10124830802ce","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想戒 有一排食少左 但慢慢又食多返</blockquote><br />\n行動吧 其實食少左之後一下停左佢好似冇咩野"},{"pid":"fcca6ef76affbea935c321b9e377de87d052bfba","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同現任散左 又食返</blockquote><br />\n只要有信念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d904782c70144d2efeace80c80535ff1b378dc1a","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T17:25:18.000Z","msg":"岩岩等女朋友放工 差啲奶野 好彩意志堅定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n訓了而家晚安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3475a5ff044de067d11330dfc310ae2c8498d1e","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:03:53.000Z","msg":"早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一朝起身好想食 幸好掉哂啲野冇破戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家唯有訓係張床道等癮過"},{"pid":"0c5edbe6be2cb1de72fd01b3ebaf29a90db5e50f","tid":456733,"uid":21006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T01:31:11.000Z","msg":"Same case，同路人，第一日"},{"pid":"8ab14171e1954db00db75e69366e0e6047aad742","tid":456733,"uid":143190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T02:19:24.000Z","msg":"起身食左枝煙 爽！"},{"pid":"dccc613fb299c780cf9d68fd19c14d6aa3efab51","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Same case，同路人，第一日</blockquote><br />\n加油，每日上黎報告"},{"pid":"dff34b02d2f05db6c4a3964ee18bf39b0bce21c1","tid":456733,"uid":155398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T10:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起身食左枝煙 爽！</blockquote><br />\n戒賭加戒煙 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b59520f5d39e3f855560c403c3af48e9be4970","tid":456733,"uid":155398,